{MY TYPICAL DAY}
My alarm wakes me around seven o'clock. I go downstairs and make my breakfast and take it into the lounge. I eat my breakfast while watching the television. About eight o'clock I go back upstairs and get dressed. After I am dressed I clean my teeth, go back downstairs, put my shoes on and take my dog for a walk. I arrive back at my house around twenty five past eight. I say "Goodbye" to my mum and dad and then I go and call for my friend. We leave her house at about twenty to nine.
